      • preProcessing

        public final void preProcessing()
        Executes the pre-proccessing method. Checks for any DisCharger and calculates the discharging time. If there is not any empty DisCharger the DisChargingEvent object is inserted in the list.

      • execution

        public final void execution()
        It starts the execution of the DisChargingEvent object. The function modifies the dischargingarray. Checks if there needs to become any update storage. Starts the discharging of the ElectricVehicle. If the DisChargingEvent object is in the list then this method does not do anything.
